text: Ian Russell may refer to: *Ian Russell (soccer) (born 1975), American soccer player *Ian Russell (rugby league) (born 1965), Australian rugby league player *Ian Russell, 13th Duke of Bedford (1917–2002), British peer and writer *Ian Russell (priest) (born 1934), Archdeacon of Coventry *Ian Russell Krauss (el mas cool) (born 2001), Chile. ==See also== *Iain Russell (born 1982), Scottish footballer
